{"tid":824819,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局宣布明天繼續停課","createTime":"2018-09-17T08:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T09:39:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f49c1f0d4161cc77934228b861da8749b6fbb4f9","tid":824819,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:48:56.000Z","msg":"由於強颱風山竹對學校造成不同程度影響，部分學校需時清理及維修校舍和設施，加上公共交通服務尚待完全恢復正常，為確保學生安全，教育局宣布明天（18日）所有學校停課。<br />\n<br />\n在安全的情況下，學校應保持校舍開放，並實施校本應急計劃，安排人手在校內安全的地方照顧有確切需要回校的學生。家長應考慮家居環境、附近的道路交通情況、學生的照顧等因素決定是否送子女回校。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180917/s00001/1537170385794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F1537170385794&d=zY%2FQSSMQZOo%2Fp9VqewScKlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=8e77c2f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F1537170385794&h=f107d239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180917/s00001/1537170385794</a>"},{"pid":"9c28c4b9e7e52d525585361febc1d3851b941799","tid":824819,"uid":51602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:49:17.000Z","msg":"都算好事"},{"pid":"f1ddf9bfcb0a4de9a8ce4f70d411c81ff1c384ca","tid":824819,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:50:38.000Z","msg":"打工仔繼續返工"},{"pid":"fac8ac6f9eb43c881af3c67f2f6eaaa28bf902bc","tid":824819,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:22:02.000Z","msg":"Ok收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e70b8fc4685bc4644b9d64aa9febf28d4b23ea","tid":824819,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g